    "title": "Urgent Opening Financial Analyst at 5paisa International Enterprises",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Financial Analyst with drive and ambition, 5paisa International Enterprises in Vadodara is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout 5paisa International Enterprises:\n5paisa International Enterprises is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Implement and maintain internal controls and audit procedures\n• Liaise with banks, regulators, and financial institutions\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n• Develop financial models and projections for business planning\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n• Coordinate with external auditors during annual audits\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Python for Finance\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in VBA\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in Income Tax\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in Power BI\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vadodara, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with 5paisa International Enterprises!",
